ion</strong>: Core open-source dataset and tools for Chinese characters, in=
cluding SVG stroke-order vector graphics, medians, and decomposition mappin=
gs for ~9,000+ common characters. The included matcher (in the demo) perfor=
ms handwriting recognition by comparing user-drawn strokes to stored stroke=
 paths.<a href=3D"https://github.com/skishore/makemeahanzi" target=3D"_blan=
k" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer nofollow" class=3D"no-copy inline text-nowrap=
